{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"symbolKind":"case","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeVertical","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"syntax":null,"code":[" If a text's language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out vertically."],"type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingMode"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingMode","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeVertical":{"abstract":[],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}]}}}